wxPython Cookbook
Chapter 5
Recipe 6 ProgressDialog

This is the example code for Recipe 6 ProgressDialog.

Prerequisites:

1) Python 2.5 or 2.6 has been installed
2) wxPython 2.8 has been installed for the version of Python used above

How to run this script:

From the command line or your IDE run the following command

python downloader.py <some_url>

example:

python downloader.py http://python.org/ftp/python/2.6.5/python-2.6.5.msi
